Package: OpenCLBayes
Type: Package
Title: A Project Template for using CMake with Rcpp
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Albrecht Gebhardt
Authors@R: person(given = "Albrecht",
                family = "Gebhardt",
                role = c("aut", "cre"),
                email = "albrecht.gebhardt@aau.at")
Maintainer: Albrecht Gebhardt <albrecht.gebhardt@aau.at>
Description: A template for building CRAN-ready R packages using Rcpp and CMake. Provides a modular structure to integrate external C/C++ libraries (e.g., OpenCL, OpenGL) in a platform-independent way. Designed for projects requiring high-performance native code without manual environment configuration or complex Makefiles.
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: OpenCL, CMake
Encoding: UTF-8
